      "text": "Here is the \"Magic Phone\", which [[Boris Shingarov]] received as a birthday present for his 4th birthday from Dr. Y. Chr. Grigoryan (a friend of our family, and my very first teacher of math and physics, and a great influence, to whom I am indebted with getting the taste for exact sciences and the corresponding mode of thinking): [http://www.shingarov.com/toys/ page]"
